ence\": \"CartService的GetCart和AddItem操作延迟显著增加，GetCart从2.0秒增至9.0秒（4.6倍），AddItem从3.6秒增至23.9秒（6.7倍）\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**根因分析关键发现：**\n\n1. **主要瓶颈**：`productcatalogservice` 是明确的根因服务，其GetProduct操作的延迟异常严重，影响了多个上游服务。\n\n2. **影响范围**：\n   - Frontend直接调用ProductCatalogService时延迟激增\n   - CheckoutService调用ProductCatalogService时也出现高延迟\n   - 整个购物流程（从浏览商品到结账）都受到影响\n\n3. **拓扑分析**：根据系统调用拓扑，ProductCatalogService是多个关键路径的下游服务，其异常会直接传播到Frontend和CheckoutService。\n\n4. **异常模式**：所有受影响的调用边都显示rrt_max（最大响应时间）异常，表明是性能瓶颈而非连接错误。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nAGREED", "log_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "25231384-574", "component": "aiops-k8s-05", "reason": "node_memory_usage_rate spike from 30.15% to 64.45% and node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes drop from 11.4GB to 5.7GB causing memory exhaustion", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "LoadMetrics(aiops-k8s-05)", "observation": "node_memory_usage_rate increased 72.52% from 30.15% to 64.45%, node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes dropped 66.8% from 11.4GB to 5.7GB"}, {"step": 2, "action": "CheckNodePodMapping()", "observation": "aiops-k8s-05 hosts productcatalogservice-1, cartservice-2, paymentservice-1 pods"}, {"step": 3, "action": "TraceAnalysis(25231384-574)", "observation": "productcatalogservice-1 GetProduct latency increased from 8.6s to 158.3s, cartservice-2 GetCart latency increased from 2.0s to 9.0s"}]}, "report_analysis_completed": true}
